Hierarchy Structure for Breaking Blue (initial plan):

Character (Abstract)
	-Player
		-gameStatus (points, level, abilities, etc)
	-Enemy

Levels (Abstract)
	-One 
		-Display (composed into all levels; foreground, background)
	-Two
	-Three
	-Four
	-ENDGAME
Master Class: Game (includes movement)
	-Breaking Blue
	-Rise of the Red
Animation (Abtract) - composed into needed classes (player, enemy)
	Abilities (Abstract)
		-Flight
		-High Jump